overview: The Teahupoo Diary takes a look at the month that was in Tahiti, including the Air Tahiti Nui Von Zipper Trials in the lead up to the Billabong Pro at Teahupoo, the worlds most prestigious event. With antics including the Papara Cheeseburger Challenge and tow-outs with Dylan Longbottom and Wade Goodall.  Plus Bonus sections including massive Tasmania.  With an all Aussie soundtrack from The Butterfly Effect, Sarah McLeod and Kleen. Free for vou from The Billabong Entertainment Division.
title: Teahupoo Diary
